text: The Swahili Wikipedia is the Swahili language version of Wikipedia. It currently has 32,000+ articles in it. It is the 91st biggest Wikipedia.The Swahili Wikipedia's grown up day after a day: See it at Meta-Wiki It is the first largest Wikipedia in Africa, followed by the Amharic Wikipedia. == References == == Other websites == * Main Page of the Swahili Wikipedia Category:Wikipedias
title: Swahili Wikipedia
